text: Angler Yukiyo Okuyama caught and released this beautiful rainbow trout using only 4-pound tippet! Okuyama landed the 9-pound, 3-ounce fish on June 29th while fly fishing the Katsura River in Japan. The current women’s 2 kg (4 lb) tippet class world record is 7 pounds, 7 ounces. pic.twitter.com/pb4AfPSRQ6
